people

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • people.Person

  • public class Person
extends java.lang.Object

    Uses an input text file to instantiate person information and then writes the person's attributes formatted to a new text file. Calculates multiple peoples average grade point average collectively.

    Since:
    1.0 (03/07/2017)
    Version:
    1.0.1 (01/13/2019)
    Author:
    Brady Lange - LinkedIn
